From ded1da09426266239ad3a069805fdd993d687b37 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: grok-build-providers-verify <verify@invalid>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 18:01:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 14/16] Apply exact file edits atomically in batches

Let search_replace accept an ordered edits array for multiple exact changes to one file. Validate every replacement against evolving in-memory content and write only once after the complete batch succeeds, so a late miss or ambiguity leaves the file untouched. Preserve the legacy single-edit wire shape, exact matching, CRLF handling, Unicode fallback, concise output, and one FileWritten notification.
